Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候了 去召集軍團吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Summon the legions. It is time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的敵人揚言要發起進攻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy vows to attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.54,0:00:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們當中有誰愿意奮起作戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who among you will stand and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.62,0:00:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們會死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一天我已經等待很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long have I awaited this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向索隆宣誓效忠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I pledge my loyalty to Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的人已經走了一半\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Half of us just left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還有一半選擇了留下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But half stayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么沒有選我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why wasn't I chosen for the expedition?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你要去西部\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought you were going west.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.70,0:00:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先做點配得上努門諾爾人做的事\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not till I've done something worthy of Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛說服努門諾爾派出五艘船\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}I have just convinced Númenor to send five ships
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和五百人來幫助你的人民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and 500 men to aid your people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.79,0:00:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你加冕為王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and place a crown upon your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.62,0:00:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在要我去一個 我發誓永遠不會回去的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are asking me to go to the one place that I swore never to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么要一直戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why do you keep fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我停不下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I cannot stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我一起去 一起拯救我們倆的種族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come with me, and together we will redeem both our bloodlines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.12,0:00:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們朝東北方向行進 前往中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We head nor'-east. For Middle-earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這并不是劍 而是一種力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is no sword. It is a power.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說過索隆嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you heard of Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前見過這個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一把鑰匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.08,0:01:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方指揮官說過 要在這些土地上給奧克一個家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The enemy commander spoke of giving the Orcs a home in these lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管他有什么陰謀 有一點是肯定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever his design, this much is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.41,0:01:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人知道你兒子 有他需要用來啟動計劃的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy knows your son has what he needs to enact it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.54,0:01:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是幾個小時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}指環王：力量之戒\N第一季第六集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外掛字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}風吹來的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  雙語合并
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔑視死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In defiance of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My children,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們經受了艱辛無數\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have endured much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們掙脫了枷鎖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cast off our shackles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越過高山和原野\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Crossed mountain, field,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.00,0:04:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過嚴寒和荒地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}frost, and fallow
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到我們腳上的血染濕了地上的泥\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}till our feet bloodied the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從灰色山脈到埃斐爾阿爾能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From Ered Mithrin to the Ephel Arnen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都堅持下來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have endured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今晚 還有一場考驗在等著我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yet tonight, one more trial awaits us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許敵人實力很弱 而且為數不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy may be weak, their numbers meager...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但明天黎明之前 我們當中會有一部分奧克倒下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...yet before this night is through, some of us will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你們這次倒下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But for the first time, 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將不再是遠方大地上籍籍無名的奴隸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you do so not as unnamed slaves in far-away lands,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是首次以兄弟的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but as brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以兄弟姐妹的身份 在屬于我們自己的土地上倒下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As brothers and sisters in our home!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat! Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就在今夜 我們將伸出烏魯克族的鐵拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the night we reach out the iron hand of the Uruk...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,握緊雙拳奪回這片土地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...and close our fist around these lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我搜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Search it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.16,0:06:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體注意 散開 把他們找出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of you! Fan out! Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 我無意冒犯 但敢問索隆在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meaning no offense, Lord-father, but where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.04,0:07:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到他的絲毫蹤跡 他肯定是學聰明逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't find tooth nor tail of him. Must've got smart and scarpered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的 那個精靈就在這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. The Elf's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聞到他的氣味了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I smell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.91,0:07:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命 父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.70,0:07:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這上邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他拿下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring him down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上撤出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那扇門打開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人 您得立刻離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lord-father! You must move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您得離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You must move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么大的火 能僥幸活下來的奧克能有多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many of 'em could have survived that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有多少時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long do we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并沒有多少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.20,0:08:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 我們得把村子武裝起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, we have to make ready the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢點 貝雷克 別激動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy, Berek. Easy, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它吊起來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hoist it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為所有士兵都上床睡覺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought all soldiers were to be abed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我 指揮官 我只是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pardon me, Commander. I... I was only...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想第一個看到大陸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hoping to get the first sight of land?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過一會兒你就能看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll be visible to your eyes in a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.87,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你已經看到了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it visible to yours already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大約一個小時前我就看到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has been for nearly an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈的眼神真是犀利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keen are the eyes of the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.91,0:10:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我卻從沒見過你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And yet, mine have not before seen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒見過你舞劍也沒見過你揚帆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swinging steel nor flying sail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么軍銜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is your rank?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我負責清掃馬廄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stable sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要瞧不起這種 能讓人學會謙遜的勞苦工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Despise not the labor which humbles the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對于整個王國來說 滿招損謙受益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Humility has saved entire kingdoms the proud have all but led to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加入遠征軍 可不是為了來學習謙遜的 指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did not join this expedition to be humbled, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你加入的目的是什么 士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then for what did you join, soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was just trying to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能遠離那個地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As far as I could from that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努門諾爾嗎\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Númenor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是努門諾爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}It's not Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不是真正的努門諾爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Not the real Númenor, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.79,0:11:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的努門諾爾根本沒存在過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If it ever existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它存在過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且仍然存在…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It exists still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕只存在于最下層的 馬廄清潔工心里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If only in the heart of the lowliest stable sweep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.12,0:11:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫伊熙爾杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's Isildur.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.20,0:11:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早該看出來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長得像你父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have the look of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們總說我長得更像我母親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was always told I look more like my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船長\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.58,0:12:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他母親…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她出什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.16,0:12:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大半輩子 望向東方都是見旭日從海面上升起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most of my life, I've looked east to see the Sun rise over the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.25,0:12:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望向西方見夕陽落到地平線下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And west to see it set over the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我們正駛向黎明 但對我而言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're sailing into the dawn, and yet, to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺卻像夜幕即將降臨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it feels like the coming of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是淹死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經看到陸地了 陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Land has been sighted, Your Majesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們多久才能拋錨停泊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long before we make anchor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要航行一整天才能進入山區\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a full day's sail into the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那里出發 要向東再騎一天才能進入山谷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And from there, another day's ride east into the vale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給其他船發信號\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Signal the other ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們盡可能加快速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell them to make all possible haste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我們的能力無法毀掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is beyond our skill to destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把它藏在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where will you hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓任何人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No one must know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連你也不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not even you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經發現了敵人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our enemy has been sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上一次我們活了下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We survived them before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.83,0:14:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我們也必將戰勝敵人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now we must do so again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.25,0:14:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的位置很有利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our position gives us an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.66,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要想利用這個優勢 必須把敵人引到近處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But to use it, we must draw the enemy in close.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須等到所有奧克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must wait until every last Orc
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.58,0:14:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨過那座橋之后 再發起進攻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has crossed that bridge to spring our attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這將會考驗你們的勇氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This will test your nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放馬過來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.37,0:15:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有無法戰斗的人員將在里邊駐守\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All who cannot fight will be barricaded inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.95,0:15:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里將是我們的要塞和撤退據點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is to be our keep. Our fallback point.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都要鼓起勇氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Take heart. All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.70,0:15:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見過許多軍隊以少勝多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have seen smaller armies defeat greater foes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽很快就要落山了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon, the sun will set.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你們保證 只要守好自己的崗位 就能見到明天的日出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do your part, and I swear to you, you shall see it rise again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你們相信嗎  -相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Do you believe it? -Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你們相信嗎  -相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Do you believe it? -Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To your positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去小酒館\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷員和兒童才去小酒館 我可以戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tavern's for wounded and children. I can fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.54,0:15:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你可以\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才要你去那里 保護無法戰斗的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why I need you in there, protecting those who cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候經常會做各種噩夢 你記得嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Remember when I was little... When I used to have bad dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得你是怎么安慰我的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You remember what you used to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你在黑暗中抱著我說的那番話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you would hold me in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在能再說給我聽嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you say it to me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“魔影終究只是渺小之物 且會逝去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"In the end, this shadow is but a small and passing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“而在魔影無法觸及之處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"There is light and high beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“光明與崇高之美永存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"forever beyond its reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.95,0:16:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“去尋找光明吧…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Find the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.50,0:16:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“如此魔影便永遠不得臨身”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"And the shadow will not find you."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.20,0:17:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Farewell, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾費林種子…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The alfirin seeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是精靈的一項傳統\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is a tradition among Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.12,0:18:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每逢戰爭開始之前 種下一顆阿爾費林種子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Before the battle begins, plant one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生命 蔑視死亡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New life, in defiance of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精靈族相信 有一位維拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It is believed that one of the Valar
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會照看生長的植物…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}watches over growing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及植物的播種者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And those who tend them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其余的種子…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們等戰爭結束后再來種\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we shall plant after the battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,種在一個新花園里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a new garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有希奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起種\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.62,0:19:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言為定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.58,0:23:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群蠢貨沒打中我們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bleeding fools missed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.37,0:23:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.75,0:23:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們正朝小酒館走去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're headed for the tavern.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-為南方大地而戰  -為南方大地而戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Fight for the Southlands! -Fight for the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.20,0:27:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片土地是我們的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The land is ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.25,0:27:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常勇敢啊 精靈 很勇敢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than a bit brave, Elf. More than a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.37,0:28:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布隆溫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bronwyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.45,0:29:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛才是在與自己人戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were fighting our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.54,0:29:19.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們以為我們會白白收留他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought we'd take 'em in for nothin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.25,0:29:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須付出代價…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had to pay the toll...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.41,0:29:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所有人都要付出代價\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now, all of you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.16,0:29:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特雷德威爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tredwill!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.75,0:30:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.54,0:30:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人 躲進要塞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone, to the keep!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.45,0:30:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.12,0:30:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進小酒館里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Into the tavern!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.37,0:30:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小酒館\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The tavern!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.75,0:30:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.16,0:30:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放桌子上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-The table!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.08,0:30:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.91,0:31:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.00,0:31:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Mother. Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.37,0:31:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先救他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.45,0:31:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.70,0:31:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會救你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.79,0:31:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.12,0:31:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希奧…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.50,0:31:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必須趕快止血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll have to stem the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.58,0:31:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I... I don't think I...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.87,0:31:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么你來止血 要么我就會死 你明白嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Either you're gonna do this or I'm gonna die. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.87,0:31:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.12,0:32:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 你做好準備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother, prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.08,0:32:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.95,0:32:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力壓住傷口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put pressure on the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.50,0:32:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燒…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Burn...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.87,0:32:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她失血過多 身體發冷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's cold. She's lost too much blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.50,0:32:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.25,0:32:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說了：“燒”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's saying "burn."
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.04,0:32:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾費林種子 我們必須用火把止住傷口出血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The alfirin seeds. We have to seal the wound with fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.62,0:32:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我拿一些點燃的木頭過來 快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bring me some burning wood. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.75,0:33:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.87,0:33:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.75,0:33:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在換這邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.12,0:33:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.00,0:33:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.91,0:33:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布隆溫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bronwyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.91,0:33:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-媽媽  -布隆溫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Mother? -Bronwyn?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.50,0:33:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒 媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wake up! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.91,0:34:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.16,0:34:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 踢他們的后背 - 戰斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Kick 'em in the back! -Nampat!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.25,0:35:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.62,0:36:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找的東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.37,0:36:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它交給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.37,0:36:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把他們放了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.75,0:36:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我才會考慮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will consider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.58,0:37:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何苦為了這么點小東西 搭上他們的性命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why sacrifice their lives for such a little thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.41,0:37:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一個是那個女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The woman next.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.29,0:37:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.04,0:37:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-等等  -希奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Wait! -Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.33,0:37:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這下邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.58,0:37:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這下邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's under here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.37,0:37:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.50,0:37:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Theo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.00,0:37:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.00,0:38:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃德雷格 我有個任務要交給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Waldreg, I have a task for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.62,0:39:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們全都得死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They all must die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.45,0:40:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安塔摩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ontamo!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.87,0:40:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.41,0:40:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.87,0:41:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.20,0:41:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.54,0:41:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.12,0:41:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我沒事 -我以為你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm all right. -I thought you...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.25,0:41:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的 伊熙爾杜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm all right, Isil.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.12,0:41:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.25,0:41:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的指揮官呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.83,0:41:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他手上的東西…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The item he possesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.12,0:41:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能讓他帶走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He must not escape with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.58,0:42:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.25,0:42:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北征軍的指揮官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander of the Northern Armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.95,0:42:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.25,0:42:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Noro lim!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.87,0:43:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.33,0:44:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你記得我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.50,0:44:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.33,0:44:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.00,0:44:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要留他一命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.87,0:44:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要留他一命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need him alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.66,0:44:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道他干過什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.58,0:44:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我傷害過你愛的人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did I cause someone you love pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.54,0:44:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個女人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.08,0:44:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是個孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.33,0:44:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Eat your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.33,0:45:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈爾布蘭德 把劍放下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Halbrand, put it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.16,0:45:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區復仇遠遠無法讓人滿足\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One cannot satisfy thirst by drinking sea water.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.70,0:45:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你覺得怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.37,0:45:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡這些山\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I like the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.08,0:45:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你馬上就能近距離看這些山了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're about to get a closer look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.54,0:45:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官加拉德瑞爾正在組建一支軍隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Commander Galadriel's putting together a company
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.04,0:45:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤逃走的奧克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to track down the Orcs that escaped,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.12,0:45:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我苦口婆心才為我們倆求得位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I managed to wheedle the pair of us a spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.75,0:45:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那安塔摩呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What about Ontamo?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.00,0:45:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我可能會 在這里待一陣子 幫幫這些人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I might stay here for a while. Lend these folk a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.54,0:45:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-這周的戰爭看夠了  -恐怕是一輩子的戰爭都看夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Seen enough battle for a week? -More like a whole lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.25,0:46:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這支軍隊什么時候出發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This company, when's it set out?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.70,0:46:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不確定 要等加拉德瑞爾先處理完阿達爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't know for certain. Not till she's done with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.54,0:46:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小的時候 聽過很多精靈被魔茍斯帶走的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was a child, I heard stories of Elves taken by Morgoth.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.00,0:46:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些精靈被折磨 被扭曲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tortured. Twisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.87,0:46:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們被改造為 一種新的 被摧殘的生命形式\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made into a new and ruined form of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.58,0:46:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是其中一員吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are one of them, are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.75,0:46:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔里昂多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Moriondor.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.00,0:46:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗之子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Sons of the Dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.83,0:46:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一批奧克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The first Orcs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.50,0:46:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏魯克族\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.04,0:46:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們更喜歡自稱“烏魯克族”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We prefer "Uruk."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.54,0:46:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連魔里昂多也是聽令于主人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even Moriondor take orders from a master.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.08,0:46:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要找你的主人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I seek yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.62,0:46:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.91,0:46:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索隆在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where is Sauron?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.08,0:47:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許我們應該讓囚犯們曬曬太陽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps we should bring our prisoners into the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.54,0:47:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔茍斯戰敗后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After Morgoth's defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.50,0:47:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們稱之為索隆的那一位…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the one you call Sauron...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.79,0:47:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致力于“治愈”中洲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Devoted himself to healing Middle-earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.75,0:47:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將被毀壞的土地 以完美的秩序重新聚攏在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}bringing its ruined lands together in perfect order.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.83,0:47:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他試圖打造一種力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He sought to craft a power
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.70,0:47:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非來源于肉體…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not of the flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.83,0:47:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是讓肉體受控于它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But over flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.70,0:47:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種不可見世界的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A power of the Unseen World.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.16,0:48:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說服盡可能多的人隨他向北行進\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He bid as many as he could to follow him far north.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.91,0:48:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但雖然他竭盡所能…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But try as he might...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.00,0:48:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是缺少一樣東西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.54,0:48:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是黑暗知識的影子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A shadow of dark knowledge
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.12,0:48:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直隱藏著 就是不讓他找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that kept itself hidden, even from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.37,0:48:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕他在求索的過程中 手上已經沾滿無數鮮血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No matter how much blood he spilt in its pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.58,0:48:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mmm. For my part...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.58,0:48:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了幫助他實現愿望 我已經犧牲了足夠多的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I sacrificed enough of my children for his aspirations.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.50,0:48:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把索隆撕碎了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I split him open.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.04,0:49:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I killed Sauron.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.79,0:49:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do not believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.08,0:49:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的整支軍隊都殺不掉索隆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You cannot believe an Uruk could do that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.29,0:49:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當然不信一個烏魯克就能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which your entire army could not.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.87,0:49:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信你是這支軍隊唯一的主人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cannot believe that you are this army's only master.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.95,0:49:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子們沒有主人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My children have no master.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.25,0:49:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不是孩子 是奴隸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They are not children, they are slaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.62,0:49:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他們每一個都有姓名 有內心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But each one has a name. A heart. A heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.37,0:49:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-由魔茍斯創造的內心 -我們都出自獨一之神的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-A heart created by Morgoth. -We are creations of The One,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.87,0:49:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出自秘火的主宰 跟你一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Master of the Secret Fire, the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.95,0:49:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也值得擁有生命之息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As worthy of the breath of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.33,0:49:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也同樣值得擁有家園\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and just as worthy of a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.16,0:49:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.70,0:49:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片土地將會是我們的 到時候你就會明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This land will be ours. Then, you will understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.87,0:49:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.29,0:50:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你族群的存在就是個錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your kind was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.83,0:50:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一群拙劣的仿制品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Made in mockery.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.29,0:50:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕要花上一整個紀元 我也會發誓要將你們斬草除根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even if it takes me all of this Age, I vow to eradicate every last one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.45,0:50:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我會讓你活著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you shall be kept alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.25,0:50:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好讓你見證那一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that one day,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.95,0:50:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候我會用匕首刺入你中毒的心臟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before I drive my dagger into your poisoned heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.16,0:50:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在你尖尖的耳朵旁低語\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will whisper in your piked ear
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.25,0:50:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的后代已經死絕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that all your offspring are dead
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.08,0:50:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你種族的禍根將以你為終結\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the scourge of your kind ends with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.04,0:50:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我不是唯一一個還活著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It would seem I'm not the only Elf alive
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.70,0:50:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已經被黑暗所改變的精靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who has been transformed by darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.79,0:50:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你苦苦尋找的魔茍斯繼任者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps your search for Morgoth's successor
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.37,0:50:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會在你的鏡子里尋見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}should have ended in your own mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.70,0:51:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我應該先殺了你 你這個奧克的奴隸販子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps I shall begin by killing you, you slavering Orc.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.50,0:51:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拉德瑞爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galadriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.58,0:51:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏魯克…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.37,0:51:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.12,0:52:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.16,0:52:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我拉了回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For pulling me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.79,0:52:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早前是你先把我拉了回來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was you, pulled me back first.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.50,0:52:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他對你做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever it was he did to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.87,0:52:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不管你做了什么…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and whatever it was you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.58,0:52:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都要放下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be free of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.66,0:52:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從不相信我能放下…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never believed I could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.08,0:52:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.95,0:53:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你并肩作戰 我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fighting at your side, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.29,0:53:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.25,0:53:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能抓住這種感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I could just hold on to that feeling,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.12,0:53:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時刻保留在我身邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}keep it with me always,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.04,0:53:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并將它深深刻入我的靈魂 那么我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}bind it to my very being, then I...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.54,0:53:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也感覺到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.66,0:53:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈爾布蘭德大人 攝政女王想見您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Lord Halbrand. The Queen Regent wishes to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.91,0:54:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝政女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Queen Regent.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.41,0:54:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你的…你讓我的人民得以幸存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I owe you... My people are alive because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.00,0:54:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照我的理解 他們之所以能活著是因為你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As I understand it, they're alive because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.00,0:54:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒想過要扛起這份重擔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A burden I never sought to take up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.83,0:55:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有極少數最優秀的領袖 才能扛此重任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Few of the finest leaders do.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.04,0:55:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你想減輕這份負擔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if you would like some relief in carrying it,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.70,0:55:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也許能幫上忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I may be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.66,0:55:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 您找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You called for me, Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.91,0:55:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布隆溫…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bronwyn...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.58,0:55:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是哈爾布蘭德大人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Lord Halbrand.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.95,0:55:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布隆溫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bronwyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.25,0:55:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎  你就是他們承諾給我們的那位國王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is it true? Are you the king we were promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.66,0:55:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.20,0:56:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.37,0:56:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向南方大地真正的國王致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail to the true King of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.33,0:56:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向南方大地真正的國王致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail to the true King of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.87,0:56:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向南方大地真正的國王致敬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All hail to the true King of the Southlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.91,0:56:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片土地上的人們 已經等待這一刻很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The men of these lands have awaited this moment a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.87,0:56:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定沒有精靈等得久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not nearly so long as the Elves.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.83,0:57:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別折磨自己了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do not torment yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.29,0:57:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換做別人 很多人也會做同樣的選擇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Many might have done the same in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.70,0:57:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.95,0:57:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到的不僅僅是內疚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not just guilt I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.83,0:57:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一種失去感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.91,0:57:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Loss?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.25,0:57:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當它在我手中時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When it was in my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.37,0:57:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感覺…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.70,0:57:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常強大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.08,0:57:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就擺脫掉它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then rid yourself of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.08,0:58:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一勞永逸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.20,0:58:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么擺脫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.33,0:58:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給努門諾爾\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}Give it to Númenor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.70,0:58:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們在返航回家的途中扔進海里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To toss into the sea on their voyage home.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.20,0:59:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放輕松 貝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Easy. Berek, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.25,0:59:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劃傷了一點而已 你沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just a scratch. You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.91,0:59:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿…貝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey, hey. Berek.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.54,0:59:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.20,0:59:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Athae...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.20,1:00:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來\N{\fn微軟雅黑\fs14}no ídhui hí.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.25,1:00:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么做到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.87,1:00:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困擾它的并不是它身上的疼痛…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not his pain that's bothering him...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.50,1:00:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是騎手的疼痛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that of his rider.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.91,1:00:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得痛啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I'm not in pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.00,1:00:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當西方之地努門諾爾的馬匹 進入戰場時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When a horse of Westernesse rides into battle,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.79,1:00:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會與騎乘的戰士 形成一種牢不可破的紐帶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he forms an unbreakable bond with the soldier he bears.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.12,1:00:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨著時間的推移 人馬合一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In time, they become as one.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.33,1:00:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至能夠了解彼此的內心深處\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even knowing the innermost feelings of each other's heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.04,1:00:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你了解它的感受  -不了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You know his feelings? -No.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.62,1:00:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它了解你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knows yours.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.29,1:00:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是從哪里學到這些的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did you learn all this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.58,1:00:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你媽媽那里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.58,1:00:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能教我嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Think you could teach me?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.33,1:01:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏頓…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ud?n... Ud?n. Ud?n.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.12,1:03:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快找掩護\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take shelter!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.87,1:03:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Queen!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.87,1:03:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝雷克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Berek!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.75,1:03:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維藍迪爾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Valandil!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.70,1:04:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻過墻去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over the wall!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.00,1:04:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-希奧  -希奧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Theo! -Theo!
